description: Fellow coffee addicts that love your caffeine fix on the go, you’ll love the brew and nomadic mood of GypsyJoe. These self-proclaimed “Roasterfarians” are serving Stafford Springs incredible craft coffee. You can enjoy their special blends fresh hot or nitro cold brewed - either way, you’re sure to be wooed. You can also find other specialty drinks and locally baked goodies at this mobile cafe.For a nomadic roast with the most, come check out Gypsy Joe Coffee!
name: GypsyJoe Coffee
